---

### 11. TESTING PATTERNS

**Provider factory test (your-provider.test.ts):**

```typescript
import { describe, it, expect, beforeEach, vi } from 'vitest';
import { createYourProvider } from './your-provider';
import { YourImageModel } from './image/your-image-model';

