```

---

### 12. KEY UTILITIES FROM @ai-sdk/provider-utils

```typescript
// API Communication
postJsonToApi()        // POST JSON and get response
getFromApi()           // GET request
postFormDataToApi()    // POST multipart form data

// Response Handling
