# @ai-sdk/pixelart

The **[PixelArt AI](https://pixelart.ai)** provider for the [AI SDK](https://ai-sdk.dev/docs) by Vercel.

It provides image generation capabilities with pixel art, retro, and 8-bit styles.

## Setup

Install the provider package:

```bash
npm install @ai-sdk/pixelart
```

Set the `PIXELART_API_KEY` environment variable with your PixelArt AI API key:

```bash
export PIXELART_API_KEY=your-api-key
```

## Provider Instance

Import the default provider instance:

```typescript
import { pixelArt } from '@ai-sdk/pixelart';
```

Or create a custom instance with `createPixelArt`:

```typescript
import { createPixelArt } from '@ai-sdk/pixelart';

const pixelArt = createPixelArt({
  apiKey: process.env.PIXELART_API_KEY,
  // Optional: override the base URL
  // baseURL: 'https://api.pixelart.ai/v1',
});
```

## Image Generation

Use `generateImage` from the `ai` package together with a PixelArt model:

```typescript
import { pixelArt } from '@ai-sdk/pixelart';
import { generateImage } from 'ai';

const { image } = await generateImage({
  model: pixelArt.image('pixel-art-v1'),
  prompt: 'A medieval castle surrounded by a moat at sunset',
  size: '512x512',
});
```

### Provider Options

Pass PixelArt-specific settings via `providerOptions.pixelart`:

```typescript
import { pixelArt } from '@ai-sdk/pixelart';
import { generateImage } from 'ai';

const { image } = await generateImage({
  model: pixelArt.image('pixel-art-v2'),
  prompt: 'A space explorer on an alien planet',
  size: '1024x1024',
  providerOptions: {
    pixelart: {
      // Style: 'pixel' | 'retro' | '8bit'
      style: 'retro',
      // Pixel cell size (1–16). Higher = chunkier pixels. Default: 4.
      pixelDensity: 8,
    },
  },
});
```

## Available Models

| Model ID         | Description                               |
| ---------------- | ----------------------------------------- |
| `pixel-art-v1`   | First-generation pixel art model          |
| `pixel-art-v2`   | Second-generation model with more detail  |
| `pixel-art-mini` | Lightweight model for fast generation     |

## Supported Parameters

| Parameter      | Support | Notes                                        |
| -------------- | ------- | -------------------------------------------- |
| `size`         | ✅      | e.g. `"512x512"`, `"1024x1024"`. Default: `"512x512"` |
| `n`            | ✅      | Up to 4 images per call                      |
| `aspectRatio`  | ⚠️      | Not supported — use `size` instead           |
| `seed`         | ⚠️      | Not supported                                |
| `files`        | ⚠️      | Image editing not supported                  |
| `mask`         | ⚠️      | Inpainting not supported                     |

## Provider-Specific Options

| Option         | Type                          | Description                         |
| -------------- | ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| `style`        | `'pixel' \| 'retro' \| '8bit'` | Artistic style for the output       |
| `pixelDensity` | `number` (1–16)               | Size of individual pixel cells      |

